{"GEIC":[{"def":"Pertaining to, or derived from, earthy or vegetable mold.","pos":""}],"GEISHA":[{"def":"A Japanese singing and dancing girl.","pos":""}],"GEISSLER TUBE":[{"def":"A glass tube provided with platinum electrodes, and containing some gas under very low tension, which becomes luminous when an electrical discharge is passed through it; -- so called from the name of a noted maker in germany.","pos":""}],"GEITONOGAMY":[{"def":"Fertilization of flowers by pollen from other flowers on the same plant.","pos":""}]}